<p>Should this property be sorted into a specific <a href="/en/item/settings/properties#1200">group</a>? If so, then select the group here.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: This drop-down list only includes property groups that were already created.
Proceed as follows to create a new group:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
