<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>).<br>
→ The properties that correspond to the search criteria entered are displayed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click in the line of the property.<br>
